Introduction

Seoho is a South Korean singer under RBW. He is a member of the boy group ONEUS.

Seoho first gained recognition for appearing on the 2017 MNET' survival show Produce 101 Season 2, where he was eliminated after ranking 94th and, in 2019, for participating in MIXNINE where he ranked 19th place and was eliminated as well.

He debuted as a member of ONEUS on January 9, 2019 with the release of their first mini album "Light Us".

On January 19, 2025 he announced that he will be enlisting in the military on February 17, 2025.
